############             default dir permissions file permissions 
for root user : 022        0777 			0666
			(-)0022                      (-)0022			
			--------		     --------	
			   0755			        0644	

umask value
############             default dir permissions file permissions
for normal user : 002      0777
			(-)0002                      0666
			--------		(-)  0002				
			   0775			 ----------  		
					             0664			

base file permission : 0666
		
